---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Cookie Policy">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p>This site utilizes standard diagnostic files known as cookies to enhance your operational flow.</p>
    <h2>How We Implement Cookies</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Preferences:</strong> To memorize specific display filters and client time configurations.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics & Ads:</strong> Third-party code networks run small trackers to display optimized promotional banners safely without accessing system core assets.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You remain free to terminate cookie configurations directly within your browser's security panel at any moment.</p>
</Layout>
